":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/12\/honor-mother-then-father\/","url_meta":{"origin":24142,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Honoring your mother, then your father","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWho is most deserving of my good company?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYour mother.\u201d The man asked, \u201cThen who?\u201d The Prophet said \u201cYour mother.\u201d The man asked again, \u201cThen who?\u201d The Prophet said, \"Your mother.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34146,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/29\/by-inspiring-good-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":24142,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Action: Allah purifies him by inspiring good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 29, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills goodness for a servant, He purifies him before his death.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the purification of the servant?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHe inspires him to perform good deeds\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/proph